Hey! Don't worry about feeling bored, here are some fun activities you can do:

1. Play video games or board games;
2. Take a nap and enjoy a good book;
3. Play your favorite music or start learning to play a new instrument;
4. Social activities or clubs;
5. Do something creative, such as calligraphy classes;
6. Start a new hobby, such as painting, knitting, pottery, etc., which can bring you relaxation and joy.
7. Listen to the radio to learn a new language;
8. Do some sports or enjoy some other exercises, such as yoga, Pilates, or jogging;
9. Enjoy some online classes, learn how to cook a new cuisine, or use a new programming language;
10. Go out to look for beautiful weather, scenery, architecture, and street life;
11. Look at some retrospective videos, photos, albums, diaries, etc., to review life;
12. Watch the movies you always want to see;
13. Try to make some new friends, or reconnect with old friends, and share your stories.

This is a great way to get back into the mood for work or entertainment. Hope you have fun!
